# OLIVINE PLATFORM — MASTER ARCHITECTURE & DEPLOYMENT REFERENCE

## 1. Overview

Olivine is an enterprise SaaS ecosystem built around a unified platform architecture.

Company
Olivine Technologies

Platform
Olivine Platform

The platform hosts multiple enterprise modules such as ERP, CRM, HRM, FMS, POS and collaboration tools.

Deployment infrastructure is hosted on AWS Elastic Beanstalk with the primary domain managed through GoDaddy.

Primary Domain
olivine.co.in

